Charlotte Maxeke was born on this day 150-years ago. Editor's note: The livestream has ended. You may watch the recording above #DStv403 #eNCA JOHANNESBURG - President Cyril Ramaphosa delivers a memorial lecture in honour of pioneering social and political activist Charlotte Maxeke.
She was born on this day 150-years ago. WATCH: Ramaphosa delivers keynote address at Winnie Madikizela-Mandela memorial Ramaphosa has described Charlotte Maxeke as a woman of outstanding leadership skills. He says one cannot talk about the history of South Africa and not talk about Maxeke.